I'm not sure what file interface you are expecting from panda. It is looking for Tell, but we have tell, which is the python FileIO interface.

>>> print dir(ff)

I'm not sure what file interface you are expecting from panda. It is looking for `Tell`, but we have `tell`, which is the python `FileIO` interface.

```
>>> f = tf.gfile.GFile('/tmp/foo.txt')
>>> print dir(f)
